{"tid":1008981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"根本voice message就係劣質文化 公眾地方開住聽仲劣質","createTime":"2019-02-05T00:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T09:46:50.000Z","uid":221265,"like":132,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"1bc0706625c82d0cb7ad26ea790c02f3d5ac4ca8","tid":1008981,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T00:29:51.000Z","msg":"3大通訊app中<br />\n支那wechat以voice message起家<br />\n當日分辨支那人其中一個方法<br />\n係見佢哋最興喺公眾地方、車內對住電話下方講講講<br />\n之後開speaker迫人聽<br />\n好多阿巫仲不斷大聲重複以上動作<br />\n<br />\n你去日本會發現日本人根本極少用voice message ,公眾地方如車內更絕對唔用<br />\n所以支那wechat 永遠入唔到日本<br />\n<br />\n日本人愛line 是like 佢可愛sticker 非voice messager <br />\n但就打入香港嘅外傭市場<br />\n好多外傭喺公共交通工具不斷講好討厭（佢哋仲好like FaceTime )<br />\n<br />\n不過香港人就越來越多人用voice message <br />\n我見親都好憎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 收到亦盡可能唔㩒入去"},{"pid":"5624a6babae939bbbc012ff434a5bc472e5e5159","tid":1008981,"uid":221265,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T00:38:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DaVNC2g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDaVNC2g.png&h=5b4ff7a7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f180aa0e2ee093c3a94174c0c455502c537f2c0","tid":1008981,"uid":73856,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T00:42:48.000Z","msg":"係 好撚on9<br />\n一眼睇到既野<br />\n係要浪費幾個動作先接收到"},{"pid":"29b83caef9b6c472bd35cba259fd6dfc6024f931","tid":1008981,"uid":221265,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9f180aa0e2ee093c3a94174c0c455502c537f2c0","tid":1008981,"uid":73856,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T00:42:48.000Z","msg":"係 好撚on9<br />\n一眼睇到既野<br />\n係要浪費幾個動作先接收到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T00:45:38.000Z","msg":"以前香港人抗拒嘅<br />\n依家似已被同化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c115ab429d7479c4daea0996e9ff19cbc56f865","tid":1008981,"uid":97240,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T00:59:51.000Z","msg":"唔明點解要開speaker聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好好地自己聽唔得既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f823cf1b2c884ef2cea227ed2b42f36f94e5254b","tid":1008981,"uid":39059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T01:08:02.000Z","msg":"唔知點解老一輩果堆硬係成日SD VM <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0112d61520503fa194887d9bd9b63e2f92664ad3","tid":1008981,"uid":39710,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T01:11:56.000Z","msg":"clutch bag + 油頭 + 勞 = 成個we7 都係voice chat 嘅金融狗地產狗唔慌好人"},{"pid":"bc58638d509c0f8a72ae5c6d1dc15ff65f1d74f6","tid":1008981,"uid":64191,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T01:16:55.000Z","msg":"通常人地voice message我都唔聽，當睇唔到"},{"pid":"243f3ff59f76333a3bd888366c9b161d76ea7d0f","tid":1008981,"uid":17245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T01:17:47.000Z","msg":"仲有好多廢中廢老傾電話係開speaker<br />\n係巴士剪指甲<br />\n根本香港已經被同化"},{"pid":"de33b6c468ea1187a6c876e2a68057f061439e99","tid":1008981,"uid":90820,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T01:23:01.000Z","msg":"voice message真係好濕鳩<br />\n最憎收到voice<br />\n又要專登拎耳筒出嚟聽你講幾秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"048bcdf8daa63d9e29a16dbc516710bc579ec335","tid":1008981,"uid":224452,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T01:32:31.000Z","msg":"其實做乜鳩唔直接打電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢啲messager就係俾你唔方便講/聽電話嘅時候text人<br />\n屌那媽港豬全部都跛手<br />\n打字係咪會死？<br />\n嫌打字慢嘅話，真係咁急趕點解又唔直接打電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d15709eb4bef762df1b80b7f4eb192de3e4b8d8","tid":1008981,"uid":132461,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T01:33:21.000Z","msg":"無知一問，voice message可唔可以當係聽電話咁聽？即係喺耳筒發聲，而唔係speaker發聲"},{"pid":"d46321ed5a1ef7bcd3f4d9f8dcfa1e60950a1401","tid":1008981,"uid":116917,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T01:34:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/opmkYk6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FopmkYk6.png&h=55036f06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55859c592d1829c0b942670eda71f9c355b9a1e0","tid":1008981,"uid":56561,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3d15709eb4bef762df1b80b7f4eb192de3e4b8d8","tid":1008981,"uid":132461,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T01:33:21.000Z","msg":"無知一問，voice message可唔可以當係聽電話咁聽？即係喺耳筒發聲，而唔係speaker發聲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T01:35:30.000Z","msg":"可以"},{"pid":"65137170172cfe1f52b83678c48eb0efcb3407cd","tid":1008981,"uid":132461,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"5624a6babae939bbbc012ff434a5bc472e5e5159","tid":1008981,"uid":221265,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T00:38:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DaVNC2g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDaVNC2g.png&h=5b4ff7a7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T01:36:01.000Z","msg":"個人認為，圖中女仔做得正確<br />\n<br />\n人地send vm，如果喺公眾地方要聽既話，正確做法係調低音量，擺埋耳度聽"},{"pid":"d03dc7240d51986dfbfa57d74977997f80fde6ac","tid":1008981,"uid":132461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"55859c592d1829c0b